# Task Card Componentization & UI Refresh

Consolidate the diverse task card implementations into a single, highly-configurable [TaskCard](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/DraggableTaskCard.tsx#38-247) component. This component will feature a modern, high-contrast light mode UI, include module/screen metadata, and remove redundant interactive elements.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The "sync squad" button currently in the task card will be removed as requested. Please confirm if there are any other interactive elements that should be simplified or removed during this refactor.

## Proposed Changes

### Dashboard Components

#### [NEW] [TaskCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/TaskCard.tsx)
- Unified component supporting:
    - Click interactions for details.
    - Drag-and-drop for squad planning.
    - Status/Category badges.
    - **Module & Screen labels** for quick overview.
    - **High-contrast Status UI** (optimized for light mode).

#### [MODIFY] [DailyMeetingView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx)
- Update [renderCard](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/NextSprintPlanningView.tsx#347-405) to use the new [TaskCard](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/DraggableTaskCard.tsx#38-247).
- Remove the `renderActions` block that contains the member toggle buttons (formerly used for squad sync).

#### [DELETE] [DraggableTaskCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/DraggableTaskCard.tsx)
- Replaced by the unified [TaskCard](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/DraggableTaskCard.tsx#38-247).

#### [MODIFY] [utils.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/utils.ts)
- Refactor [statusBadge](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/utils.tsx#171-185) and [priorityDotColor](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/utils.tsx#162-170) to use high-contrast, light-mode friendly styles (e.g., using solid colors for dots and tinted backgrounds for badges).

